Class GameEndScreen

java.lang.Object
com.badlogic.gdx.ScreenAdapter
com.group4.Auber.GameEndScreen
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.badlogic.gdx.Screen
public class GameEndScreen
extends com.badlogic.gdx.ScreenAdapter
GameEndScreen is an extension of ScreenAdapter to create and render the end game screen.
Author:
Bogdan Bodnariu-Lescinschi
